{"article_id":"EsotP4gDMv2WN5ZP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Orrin Hatch and Amy Klobuchar sponsored the amendment .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"|","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"AP Photos","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Dems join push","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"to dump health tax","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Thirty-four Senate Democrats joined Republicans on Thursday night in a nonbinding but overwhelming vote","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to repeal a key tax in President Barack Obama 's health reform law .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"The Senate voted 79-20 to get rid of the law 's 2.3 percent sales tax on medical device-makers .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The amendment to the budget resolution wo n't become law","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"because the budget is nonbinding .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"But it has huge political significance","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"as momentum builds for bipartisan consensus","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"to get rid of another piece of Obamacare .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"This levy was supposed to help pay for $ 29 billion of the costs of the law .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"But the medical device industry has raised a raucous over the tax ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"slowly building support","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to eliminate it .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"The tax went into effect in January .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Assuming none of the provision 's backers rescind their support ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"there is now plenty of support","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to surpass the 60 votes","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"needed","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"to repeal the device tax","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"if it comes to a vote , on another bill in the future .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Thirty-three Democrats and one independent","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"who caucuses with them","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"supported the measure .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"The Democrats","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who backed the repeal","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"include Sens . Dick Durbin of Illinois , Chuck Schumer of New York , Maria Cantwell of Washington , Barbara Mikulski of Maryland , Tim Kaine of Virginia , Elizabeth Warren of Massachusetts and nearly all Democrats from states with many device-makers , such as Pennsylvania , Minnesota and Indiana .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"But Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"( D-Nev. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"who controls which legislation gets votes ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and Senate Finance Committee Chairman Max Baucus","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"( D-Mont . ) ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"whose committee wrote the tax ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"voted against the measure .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Republicans have long railed against the tax ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"they say","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"stifles innovation in the medical device industry .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"They say","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that the tax is particularly unjust","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"because it taxes sales and not profits ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"so startup and struggling companies will be taxed just like thriving established companies .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" The importance of this vote can not be overstated , ''","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"said Sen. Orrin Hatch","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"( R-Utah ) ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"who introduced the amendment and a similar bill in the last Congress .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"`` For the first time , Democrats and Republicans have come together","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"in recognizing how bad this tax is .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"We can not stop here .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"We must continue the fight","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"to get rid of this tax . ''","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Democrats have slowly started to support the measure in larger numbers .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"In December , 19 Democrats signed on to a letter","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"asking Reid to delay the tax .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"`` We can not have taxes","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"that put as at a competitive disadvantage '' against the rest of the world , ''","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"said Sen. Amy Klobuchar of Minnesota , the lead Democrat on the amendment .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"The amendment was co-sponsored by eight other Democrats , most from states with many device-makers .","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"This article first appeared on Pro at 9:48 p.m. on March 21 , 2013 .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":62,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":67,"right":123,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":0,"right":64,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":116,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":107,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":79,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":69,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":73,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":70,"right":72,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":10,"right":71,"relation":"cont